{"tid":1829073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲首領大波Man首默認 黃色經濟圈 與 五大訴求","createTime":"2020-01-18T12:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T02:30:19.000Z","uid":28114,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"328004ad89b76c26caa2a43b254eb5ce02bff5f5","tid":1829073,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"昨日凌晨身穿 #全黑套裝 既大波man於元朗街頭遇見一眾黃色商戶聚餐，起始大波man一心單挑黃色勢力，￼可惜被一眾腦細質問警暴與濫權後之吾以對，並最後對於警暴問題回答 #絕不支持任何暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n並且對於黃色勢力既團結與人情味感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n￼奉政府諭請立即停止一切暴力行為，包括警隊與支持政府陣營，珍惜香港，聆聽主流民意<br />\n<br />\n收手啦，藍色惡勢力，有相為證。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n#關公大戰外星人<br />\n#水門痴撚線日常￼￼<br />\n#好人好姐著黑色？<br />\n#明眼人都知佢暗黃<br />\n#仲飲燉湯？<br />\n#燉湯無牌架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htUXE3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtUXE3a.jpg&h=85bcb27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/737261133131865/posts/1230110573846916/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F737261133131865%2Fposts%2F1230110573846916%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1GXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=833e7c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/737261133131865/posts/1230110573846916/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"ee73ce5f86c824d4b8e102836925872870c14718","tid":1829073,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"之吾以對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字都打撚錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a35ed96f250c886e84e3298d5c8c416c993634","tid":1829073,"uid":58453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"堅定流呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11014df846c6b34433854f8d7c71a9ca467a1f9e","tid":1829073,"uid":104